exports[`Premed Atlas export serializers > serializes seed data to Markdown grouped by pillar 1`] = `
"# Premed Atlas Export

Exported: 2026-07-14T00:00:00.000Z

## Prerequisites and Course Planning

### Most US MD programs require one year of biology with laboratory work.

> Most medical schools require one academic year of biology with laboratory experience.

Evidence | Country Specific | Official Organization | Official | Officially Verified | Current | 0.97
-- *AAMC: Premedical coursework requirements overview* (aamc.org)

## MCAT

### Sources disagree on MCAT timeline: a long part-time runway versus short full-time dedicated prep. Both can work; the fit depends on work obligations, burnout risk, and content retention.

Concept | Universal | Unknown Or Self Reported | Unknown | Disputed | Current | 0.90

### Spread MCAT preparation over about six months if working or in classes.

> I get asked constantly whether you can prep for the MCAT while working full-time. I did, and it took me six months.

Advice | Applicant Specific, Financial Situation Specific | Physician | Professional Experience | Disputed | Current | 0.80
-- *Why I studied for the MCAT over 6 months (while working)* (YouTube) @ 0:12

### Study for the MCAT in roughly three months of full-time dedicated prep rather than a long stretched timeline.

> 3 months full-time or don't bother. Long timelines just mean you forget the first chapters by test day.

Advice | Applicant Specific | Premed Student | Anecdotal | Disputed | Current | 0.75
-- *r/MCAT: 3 months full-time or don't bother* (Reddit)

## Clinical Experience

### Applicants need at least 500 clinical hours to apply.

> You need at least 500 clinical hours to apply. That's the floor.

Advice | Applicant Specific | Medical Student | Anecdotal | Unverified | Probably Current | 0.55
-- *How many clinical hours you ACTUALLY need* (TikTok) @ 0:18

### Keep a reflection journal after every clinical shift.

> Keep a journal after every shift — you will forget the patients that mattered by the time you write your personal statement.

Advice | Universal | Medical Student | Professional Experience | Unverified | Current | 0.85
-- *How many clinical hours you ACTUALLY need* (TikTok) @ 0:58

### No universal minimum clinical hour requirement exists; treat quoted thresholds as one person's heuristic.

> You need at least 500 clinical hours to apply.

Warning | Universal | Unknown Or Self Reported | Unknown | Unverified | Current | 0.70
-- *How many clinical hours you ACTUALLY need* (TikTok) @ 0:18

### Clinical experience must involve real patient contact to count.

> It has to be real patient contact. Stocking shelves in a hospital gift shop does not count.

Concept | Universal | Medical Student | Community Consensus | Community Supported | Current | 0.82
-- *How many clinical hours you ACTUALLY need* (TikTok) @ 0:42

## Research

### Cold-email principal investigators with a specific reference to their recent work and a clear, small ask.

> Don't send a generic template. Mention the paper of theirs you actually read and ask for fifteen minutes.

Advice | Universal | Physician | Professional Experience | Community Supported | Current | 0.88
-- *Getting into research with zero connections (podcast)* (Podcast) @ 5:12

### Publications are not required for MD applicants; sustained engagement matters more.

> The vast majority of successful applicants have zero publications. What committees want is evidence you engaged with the process.

Advice | Country Specific | Physician | Community Consensus | Community Supported | Current | 0.86
-- *Getting into research with zero connections (podcast)* (Podcast) @ 18:25

## Letters of Recommendation

### Ask for recommendation letters while the relationship is active, not years later.

> Ask before you leave the class. Your professor remembers you right now — in two years you're a name on a roster.

Advice | Universal | Applicant | Community Consensus | Community Supported | Current | 0.90
-- *Ask for letters BEFORE you leave the class* (Instagram) @ 0:08

## Personal Statement and Story Bank

### Show growth through patient stories rather than listing achievements.

Concept | Universal | Advisor | Community Consensus | Community Supported | Current | 0.85

### My hospice patient Ms. R taught me that presence matters more than procedure — a moment I want to open my personal statement with.

Reflection | Applicant Specific | Premed Student | Anecdotal | Unverified | Current | 1.00

## Financial Planning

### The White Coat Investor blog and book cover physician-specific debt, insurance, and investing basics.

Resource | Universal | Financial Professional | Professional Experience | Community Supported | Probably Current | 0.90

## Actions

- [ ] Ask Dr. Rivera for a letter before June
  Organic chemistry relationship is active now; ask before the semester ends. Bring a résumé and a draft of the personal statement.

## Contradictions

- Spread MCAT preparation over about six months if working or in classes. <> Study for the MCAT in roughly three months of full-time dedicated prep rather than a long stretched timeline.
  Long part-time runway vs. short full-time dedicated prep.
"
`;

